    title: 'Beyond Parental Controls: Teaching Kids Responsible Digital Communication in Safe Messaging Apps',
    category: 'Elder Safety',
    excerpt: 'Go beyond app features. Learn practical strategies to teach your child responsible digital communication, empathy, and etiquette within safe messaging apps.',
    metaDescription: 'Go beyond app features. Learn practical strategies to teach your child responsible digital communication, empathy, and etiquette within safe messaging apps.',
    readTime: 7,
    date: 'April 2026',
    packageId: 'aging',
